      • UNICAST

      • MULTICAST

      • MULTICAST_SEQUENTIAL

        public static final NotificationMetadata.NotificationModel MULTICAST_SEQUENTIAL

      • MULTICAST_PARALLEL

        public static final NotificationMetadata.NotificationModel MULTICAST_PARALLEL
